And then, come to blast Antichrist, and to consume that Man of Sinne; 
               2 Thess. 2. 3. and so make way for the other degree of thy comming: Come in the fulnesse


of the Gentiles, come in the conversion of thy people of the Iewes, that their Riches may be an encrease of our Riches, that there may be golden times indeed; as surely then they will be.
